    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead">Date Management Tool</span></p>
<div class="page">
<div class="layoutArea">
<div class="column">
<p><strong>What does it do?</strong></p>
<p>This tool allows tutors to view in one screen when items are available and change dates attached to more than one content item within a module at the same time. For example, change:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>adaptive release dates on content, lesson plans, folders, files, web links, tasks, mash-ups and the due date of assessments</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>dates when discussion boards are visible</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Announcement start and close dates</p>
<p>The tool also provides an overview of date criteria set against all items within your module.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></Value>
